![á„‰á…³á„á…³á„…á…µá†«á„‰á…£á†º 2025-11-16 á„‹á…©á„’á…® 9.48.36.png](%EC%B5%9C%EC%9E%A5%20%EC%A6%9D%EA%B0%80%20%EC%88%98%EC%97%B4(LIS)/%E1%84%89%E1%85%B3%E1%84%8F%E1%85%B3%E1%84%85%E1%85%B5%E1%86%AB%E1%84%89%E1%85%A3%E1%86%BA_2025-11-16_%E1%84%8B%E1%85%A9%E1%84%92%E1%85%AE_9.48.36.png)

